Package: zashboard
Title: Build Dashboards from One Spec as Static HTML, Shiny, or Shinylive
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zobaer", "Ahmed", , "zobaer09@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build production dashboards from a single declarative spec into four targets: static HTML, a Shiny app, a Shinylive app, and a Quarto site. Includes helpers for local analytics (DuckDB, Arrow) and Microsoft SQL Server through DBI/ODBC, plus theming via bslib and simple build automation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
